window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>To expand my territory, I have to get married. Again.</p> <p>Everything has been great. Great ship. Great relationships. Great—well, you know.</p> <p>But when the flagship runs into trouble out in unexplored space, I've got a debt to repay. And so does my wife: Zenna.</p> <p>Now all bets are off as we race to rescue a species with ties to the Elderin's past, and our future. That means learning a new language, blowing things up, and picking the best prospects the galaxy has to offer.</p>"; 
